<li><strong>Blood test:</strong> <a href="https:///labs/test/complete-blood-count-1717?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Edema_factbox_0_necessary_tests_5_direct_link_0">complete blood count (CBC)</a> along with <a href="https:///labs/test/kidney-function-test-2561?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Edema_factbox_0_necessary_tests_5_direct_link_1">kidney function test</a>, l<a href="https:///labs/test/lipid-profile-1909?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Edema_factbox_0_necessary_tests_5_direct_link_2">ipid profile</a> and <a href="https:///labs/test/liver-function-test-2562?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Edema_factbox_0_necessary_tests_5_direct_link_3">liver function test</a></li>
