<p dir="ltr"><strong>Beta-blockers:</strong> <a href="https:///generics/propranolol-210570?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Excessive sweating_factbox_0_treatment_5_direct_link_3">Propranolol</a></p>
